fields.value: Cochrane Rehabilitation "tagging" of Cochrane Reviews 1996 - August 2018

authorAffiliation.value: Department of Rehabilitation Medicine PNS Shifa Hospital
IRCCS Fondazione Don Carlo Gnocchi and Clinical and Experimental Sciences Department, University of Brescia

dsDescriptionValue.value: This dataset contains all reviews and protocols published by Cochrane (titles, abstracts and URLs), screened by the Cochrane Rehabilitation Review Committee, and 'tagged' for relevance to rehabilitation, professional groups involved, and broad clinical area.  Duplicate publications (including completed reviews published after a published protocol and updated reviews published during the screening period) are highlighted in column F based on Access Number.  Last updated 17 November 2018.

files.description: This file contains all Cochrane reviews and protocols screened by the Cochrane Rehabilitation Review Committee for relevance to “rehabilitation”.  Titles and abstracts for reviews and protocols published by Cochrane between 1996 to August 2018 were uploaded in separate 'lots' (each 'lot' being a year of Cochrane publications), with the Review Committee completing this work between August 2017 and September 2018.  As such, this database includes 488 Cochrane reviews and protocols that were republished (either as protocols that become full reviews or as reviews that were updated) between August 2017 and September 2018.  Republished reviews and protocols can be identified by "Access Number" (Column F).
